	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2234638378" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2234638378" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Thanks Philipp! I think I've got it fixed now - check out the last code block. Was it just that missing /logs line in .gitignore of the last code block, or was there something else wrong too? I wasn't totally sure - but let me know!</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
	                </li>
	            	                <li class="dsq-comment dsq-clearfix" data-dsq-comment-id="2229632821" id="dsq-comment-2229632821">
