	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2229632821" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2229632821" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Great tutorial, thanks!<br>2 small things in the script: "/logs" path is missing the last listing of ".gitignore" file and the code listings sum up the line with one additional line (e.g. 3 lines for the .gitignore file instead of 2).</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
